{"tid":1999591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"各位sigma fans呢幾日dse考成典?","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T17:01:58.000Z","uid":76115,"like":68,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe4b96170550c653b51c9a58522b8c4dd7bbb10","tid":1999591,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"考通識嗰陣覺得啲題目冇乜空間畀我發揮嚴密邏輯同尖銳嘅社會批評<br />\n嬲嬲地寫唔出野, 開考半粒鐘走咗<br />\n幫我收卷個監考員廿幾碎囡隔住罩都睇到化行哂妝, 係咁同我有眼神接觸, 我心諗mk妹又想收兵, 好在我睇過the great gasby (條sigma解讀片) 一早洞悉兩性關係人類心理唔中你計<br />\n出到考場喺wts group留言「好撚悶 走咗」, 兩粒鐘後即刻個個話「使唔使咁勁 半粒鐘做完」、「你靠其他科都入三大啦」, 我一睇就知班撚樣想捧殺我, 冷笑咗下就禁咗退group<br />\n頭先悶悶地做份chem past paper玩下, 同啲垃圾教畜答案對下居然零分, 即刻諗起sigma講過傳統老師都係呃飯食, 我得閒上youtube睇下啲電影game解釋science片一樣做到化學家, 不禁覺得傳統教育呢個遊戲真係消磨心智, 可能最後都係考英文晒下我句HUGE SHOUTOUT TO XXX FOR YYY算鳩數"},{"pid":"574bdcd80b8cacd0e24ceedc81bb4e3a986e1d5d","tid":1999591,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33fc85f2e0cc78ebb71b1296d7636e8bfd4a2ed","tid":1999591,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"f6cb4e3ab01c24b57674a40a71da2d05be42b963","tid":1999591,"uid":48317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4025d848d1037204bec83c1d003f04a2fbe2b0d","tid":1999591,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CLS"},{"pid":"7701a0992e4cd8b8fcd43985ae3db6424e6d619f","tid":1999591,"uid":76115,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"d4025d848d1037204bec83c1d003f04a2fbe2b0d","tid":1999591,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03